name: Dark waters/ Thoughts focused on a single goal #4
description: Dark Waters is a series of drawings that attempt to represent states of my mind during meditation processes. They manifest energetic shocks, spatial translations, explosions of color and packets of information that happen in my psyche during transcendent processes. Thoughts focused on a single goal show the way my objectives are represented in my psique during meditation states.  Always shining and changing, as spheres of concepts lined by my will.
